title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On March 30, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190114443 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. If you need assistance, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you change your mailing address, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

body: On March 31, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190114729 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee.
